<paragraph blockId="5.[113,1089,1334,1581]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Stal, 1861" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1861" box="[256,437,1334,1357]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Tylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[256,327,1334,1357]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Tylana</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="STAL C." box="[331,437,1334,1357]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="195 - 223" refId="ref3891" refString="STAL C. 1861: Nova methodus familias quasdam Hemipterorum disponendi. Ofversigt af Kongliga Svenska Vetenskaps-Akademiens Forhandlingar 18 (4): 195 - 223." type="journal article" year="1861">Stål, 1861</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was erected for species from the Mascarenes (
<collectingCountry box="[912,1017,1334,1357]" name="Mauritius" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Mauritius</collectingCountry>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="STAL C." pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="195 - 223" refId="ref3891" refString="STAL C. 1861: Nova methodus familias quasdam Hemipterorum disponendi. Ofversigt af Kongliga Svenska Vetenskaps-Akademiens Forhandlingar 18 (4): 195 - 223." type="journal article" year="1861">STÅL 1861</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="WILLIAMS J. R." box="[178,340,1366,1389]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="43 - 56" refId="ref3961" refString="WILLIAMS J. R. 1982: Issidae (Hemiptera: Fulgoroidea) from the Mascarenes. Journal of Entomological Society of South Africa 45: 43 - 56." type="journal article" year="1982">WILLIAMS 1982</bibRefCitation>
). The genus needs revision as already mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation author="WILLIAMS J. R." box="[884,1064,1366,1389]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="43 - 56" refId="ref3961" refString="WILLIAMS J. R. 1982: Issidae (Hemiptera: Fulgoroidea) from the Mascarenes. Journal of Entomological Society of South Africa 45: 43 - 56." type="journal article" year="1982">WILLIAMS (1982)</bibRefCitation>
. It is probably monotypical as its 
<typeStatus box="[431,477,1398,1421]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">type</typeStatus>
species, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Fabricius, 1803)" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1803" box="[571,918,1398,1421]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Tylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cristata">
<emphasis box="[571,729,1398,1421]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Tylana cristata</emphasis>
(Fabricius, 1803)
</taxonomicName>
, is very peculiar and differs from other species assigned to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1861" box="[549,621,1430,1453]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Tylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[549,621,1430,1453]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Tylana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the metope narrow between eyes, with no intermediate carinae and the coryphe with leaf-shaped lateral margins (
<bibRefCitation author="WILLIAMS J. R." box="[867,1033,1462,1485]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="43 - 56" refId="ref3961" refString="WILLIAMS J. R. 1982: Issidae (Hemiptera: Fulgoroidea) from the Mascarenes. Journal of Entomological Society of South Africa 45: 43 - 56." type="journal article" year="1982">WILLIAMS 1982</bibRefCitation>
: 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figs 1–7" captionStartId="2.[151,188,1506,1525]" captionTargetBox="[151,1114,229,1455]" captionTargetId="figure-10@2.[151,1126,219,1085]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="Figs 1–7. Orthophana (Eupharos) tamdaoina sp. nov., holotype. 1 – lateral view; 2 – dorsal view; 3 – hind wing; 4 – frontal view. 5–7 – apex of female abdomen (5 – lateral view; 6 – dorsal view; 7 – caudal view)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4503845" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4503845/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Figs 1–3</figureCitation>
). Based on this feature of the coryphe 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1861" box="[567,639,1494,1517]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Tylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[567,639,1494,1517]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Tylana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
may be closely related to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1954" box="[919,1017,1494,1517]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Epitonga" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[919,1017,1494,1517]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Epitonga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="54" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,1089,1334,1581]" lastBlockId="7.[113,1088,916,1035]" lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="54" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">
Our study of 
<taxonomicName authority="Walker, 1862" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1862" box="[278,581,1526,1549]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Issus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lineolatus">
<emphasis box="[278,439,1526,1549]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Issus lineolatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="WALKER F." box="[443,581,1526,1549]" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="303 - 319" refId="ref3918" refString="WALKER F. 1862: Characters of undescribed species of Homoptera in the collection of F. P. Pasco, F. L. S. The Journal of Entomology Descriptive and Geographical 1: 303 - 319, plate 15." type="journal article" year="1862">Walker, 1862</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[641,765,1526,1549]" country="Australia" name="Queensland" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Queensland</collectingRegion>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[794,893,1526,1549]" name="Australia" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Australia</collectingCountry>
, placed by 
<bibRefCitation author="DISTANT W. L." pageId="5" pageNumber="52" pagination="73 - 87" refId="ref3473" refString="DISTANT W. L. 1909: Rhynchotal notes. XLVIII. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 8 4: 73 - 87." type="journal article" year="1909">DISTANT (1909)</bibRefCitation>
to the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1861" box="[331,403,1558,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Tylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[331,403,1558,1581]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Tylana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, shows that this species actually belongs to the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1954" box="[991,1089,1558,1581]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Cotylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="52" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[991,1089,1558,1581]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="52">Cotylana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
which was erected by 
<bibRefCitation author="FENNAH R. G." box="[364,526,916,939]" pageId="7" pageNumber="54" pagination="455 - 474" refId="ref3529" refString="FENNAH R. G. 1954: The higher classification of the family Issidae (Homoptera: Fulgoroidea) with descriptions of new species. Transactions of the Royal Entomological Society of London 105: 455 - 474." type="journal article" year="1954">FENNAH (1954)</bibRefCitation>
for another Australian species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Kirkaldy, 1906" authorityName="Kirkaldy" authorityYear="1906" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Lollius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acutipennis">
<emphasis box="[881,1088,916,939]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="54">Lollius acutipennis</emphasis>
Kirkaldy, 1906
</taxonomicName>
, and to which some species from 
<collectingCountry box="[642,807,948,971]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="7" pageNumber="54">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
were later added (
<bibRefCitation author="FENNAH R. G." pageId="7" pageNumber="54" pagination="1 - 116" refId="ref3568" refString="FENNAH R. G. 1969: Fulgoroidea (Homoptera) from New Caledonia and the Loyalty Islands. Pacific Insects Monograph 21: 1 - 116." type="journal article" year="1969">FENNAH 1969</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fennah" authorityYear="1954" box="[190,288,980,1003]" class="Insecta" family="Nogodinidae" genus="Cotylana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[190,288,980,1003]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="54">Cotylana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished within the tribe 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kirkaldy" authorityYear="1907" box="[646,729,980,1003]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Tongini">Tongini</taxonomicName>
by a tricarinate metope (
<figureCitation box="[1002,1080,980,1003]" captionStart="Figs 14–15" captionStartId="6.[151,188,1562,1581]" captionTargetBox="[151,1126,1078,1545]" captionTargetId="figure-42@6.[151,1126,1077,1545]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Figs 14–15. Cotylana lineolata (Walker, 1862). 14 – lateral view, 15 – frontal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4503851" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4503851/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="54">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
) and wide fore wings with reticulate venation (
<figureCitation box="[604,683,1012,1035]" captionStart="Figs 14–15" captionStartId="6.[151,188,1562,1581]" captionTargetBox="[151,1126,1078,1545]" captionTargetId="figure-42@6.[151,1126,1077,1545]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Figs 14–15. Cotylana lineolata (Walker, 1862). 14 – lateral view, 15 – frontal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4503851" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4503851/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="54">Fig. 14</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
